{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":236410,"duration_api_ms":207299,"num_turns":27,"result":"```json\n{\n  \"change_summary\": \"Removed snapshot-based plan_hash backfill from all code paths that touch existing rows (both open and terminal), retaining it only for new entry creation where the current snapshot is definitionally correct. This addresses both amendments: (1) A legacy open row with plan_hash=None can no longer be mislabeled with a newer snapshot hash after plan evolution — the backfill at fs.rs:2914-2921 (backfill_running_entry path) and fs.rs:3246-3249 (non-terminal finalization path) was removed, with explanatory comments documenting the rationale. (2) The terminal-replay repair path through backfill_terminal_entry intentionally does not auto-populate plan_hash from the snapshot either, for the same plan-evolution safety reason — a legacy finalized row with plan_hash=None stays None when replayed with plan_hash=None. Added 2 regression tests using preseeded TaskRunEntry rows via append_task_run to exercise both scenarios across plan evolution.\",\n  \"steps\": [\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Removed snapshot-based plan_hash backfill from backfill_running_entry path in record_task_run_start (fs.rs:2914-2921). Replaced with explanatory comment: persist_plan() can advance snapshot.plan_hash after the original attempt started, so stamping the current hash would mislabel a v1 attempt as v2\",\n      \"order\": 1,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Removed snapshot-based plan_hash backfill from non-terminal finalization path in update_task_run (fs.rs:3246-3249). Same rationale: existing open rows must not be mislabeled after plan evolution\",\n      \"order\": 2,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Verified new entry creation path in record_task_run_start (fs.rs:2944-2950) retains snapshot auto-population — this is the only safe location because a brand new entry is definitionally running under the current plan\",\n      \"order\": 3,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Confirmed backfill_terminal_entry (fs.rs:2670-2703) correctly does not auto-populate from snapshot — it only copies caller-supplied values, and callers pass None through from the service layer. No code change needed\",\n      \"order\": 4,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added regression test legacy_open_row_without_plan_hash_not_mislabeled_after_plan_evolution: preseeds a Running entry with plan_hash=None via append_task_run, persists a plan (snapshot gains hash_v1), replays start then completion with plan_hash=None — asserts plan_hash stays None at both stages\",\n      \"order\": 5,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added regression test terminal_replay_legacy_row_without_plan_hash_stays_unset: preseeds a Succeeded entry with plan_hash=None and outcome_detail=None, persists a plan, replays terminal completion with plan_hash=None — asserts plan_hash stays None while outcome_detail is backfilled to 'repair detail'\",\n      \"order\": 6,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Ran cargo test (1163 total: 351 lib + 128 integration + 1 doc + 683 unit, all pass), cargo clippy -- -D warnings (clean), cargo fmt --check (modified files clean)\",\n      \"order\": 7,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"validation_evidence\": [\n    \"cargo test: 1163 total tests passed (351 lib + 128 integration + 1 doc + 683 unit), 0 failed\",\n    \"cargo clippy -- -D warnings: no warnings or errors\",\n    \"cargo fmt --check: service.rs and fs.rs pass; only pre-existing formatting diffs in unrelated tests/unit/agent_execution_test.rs\",\n    \"legacy_open_row_without_plan_hash_not_mislabeled_after_plan_evolution: preseeds Running entry with plan_hash=None, persists plan, replays start → plan_hash stays None; completes → plan_hash stays None\",\n    \"terminal_replay_legacy_row_without_plan_hash_stays_unset: preseeds Succeeded entry with plan_hash=None, persists plan, replays terminal completion → plan_hash stays None, outcome_detail backfilled to 'repair detail'\",\n    \"plan_hash_auto_populated_from_snapshot (from round 1): still passes — new entry creation auto-populates from snapshot, completion preserves the already-set hash\",\n    \"start_replay_after_plan_evolution_does_not_conflict (from round 2): still passes — row with hash_v1 is not overwritten by snapshot hash_v2 on replay\",\n    \"terminal_replay_after_plan_evolution_succeeds (from round 2): still passes — terminal replay with plan_hash=None does not conflict with stored hash_v1\",\n    \"All 8 previous round tests continue to pass unchanged\"\n  ],\n  \"outstanding_risks\": [\n    \"Pre-existing formatting drift in tests/unit/agent_execution_test.rs is unrelated to these changes but will appear in cargo fmt --check across the full workspace.\"\n  ]\n}\n```","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"dc6aa508-19dd-4e12-bdf9-726d7fd9c018","total_cost_usd":2.7405269999999997,"usage":{"input_tokens":24,"cache_creation_input_tokens":141290,"cache_read_input_tokens":3196789,"output_tokens":10358,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":141290,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":24,"outputTokens":10358,"cacheReadInputTokens":3196789,"cacheCreationInputTokens":141290,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":2.7405269999999997,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":64000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"841fd67b-9a8e-4535-9339-a87e697020f7"}
